description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'DAY 7 Back to Basics - 15 MIN FULL BODY STRETCH For Rest Day, Improve Mobility & Flexibility' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Day 7 / 14-Day BACK TO BASICS CHALLENGE - Recover on your rest day with this 15 min Full Body Stretch. Take it slow for your body and mind so you're feeling fresh and recharged - ready for another new week of workouts! Enjoy every second of it Team!

♡ SPECIAL YOUTUBE CHALLENGE OFFER: Sign Up for a 1 Month Free Trial for my GROW WITH ANNA APP: https://growwithanna.com/pages/youtube ♡ 

▸ Focus: Recovery & Mobility
▸ Time: 15 Min
▸ Equipment: No Equipment
▸ Workout: 50 sec on, 10 sec off to change to the next stretch ♡ 

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
